→ users
→ businesses
→ business_members
→ business_onboarding
→ onboarding_steps
→ agent_settings
```

Semua insert harus dalam satu Prisma transaction.

### Output minimal

```json
{
  "user": { "id": "uuid", "name": "Owner", "email": "owner@mail.com" },
  "business": { "id": "uuid", "name": "Kopi Senja", "status": "onboarding" },
