# Ningki AI Engine

AI Engine untuk Ningki WhatsApp AI CRM.

## Responsibilities

- Onboarding agent
- WhatsApp customer agent
- Knowledge agent
- CRM assistant agent
- RAG retrieval
- Tool orchestration
- Guardrail
