```

API insert:

```txt
reservations
customers.totalReservations++
customers.leadStatus=reserved
notifications type=new_reservation
```

Admin dashboard:

```txt
GET /reservations
POST /reservations/:id/confirm
POST /reservations/:id/cancel
```

