## 5.8 Order via AI tool

AI memanggil API tool endpoint:

```txt
POST /internal/tools/orders
```

API transaction:

```txt
orders
order_items
orders.totalAmount
customers.totalOrders++
customers.leadStatus=ordered
notifications type=new_order
